{"tid":446741,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞][美腿]生命有冇take 2? (原曲: 披風)","createTime":"2017-10-24T14:50:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T14:26:53.000Z","uid":2350,"like":12,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ac86a0f6ca292b2229862de8b9dbc2dea19793","tid":446741,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qfh5xomb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqfh5xomb&h=eb8d2ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Hm6d-9R2wxk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHm6d-9R2wxk&d=BE8umleqyV4iKsUKwd3M4%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e9748fe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Hm6d-9R2wxk</a><br />\n聽歌link: <br />\n原曲：披風<br />\n作詞：易家揚<br />\n作曲：MJ 譚傑明、Jerald<br />\n編曲：Jerald<br />\n<br />\n改詞：凱笑<br />\n主唱：Rider.<br />\n<br />\n歌詞：<br />\n<strong>生與死 已聽過太多 等到死再撕破真偽<br />\n雲上那個你遠在天際 所以是個迷<br />\n想結果 種起了再多 隨機作廢<br />\n有一種難題 無論錯與對畢竟只會過一世<br />\n<br />\n微笑亦帶著三分沮喪 捱再累也別仰望曙光<br />\n縱使迷惘 若是安躺 也不妨入睡放棄出汗<br />\n在呼吸中只可跌到強壯 <br />\n只當玩笑一樁<br />\n或會心安<br />\n<br />\n得到的要不要放低 失去的會不會安慰<br />\n還自信答案放在天際 暫時別再提<br />\n想結果 錯失了再多 仍想說人生有後遺<br />\n然後閉上眼偷走 走到那一世<br />\n<br />\n微笑亦帶著三分沮喪 捱再累也別仰望曙光<br />\n縱使迷惘 若是安躺 也不妨入睡放棄出汗<br />\n再辛苦都不可以太難看 總要自製心安<br />\n<br />\n能過活也是一單慘案 何以念掛著救命處方<br />\n結束迷惘 亦是不枉 有天能入睡當作解放<br />\n既講了晚安 便要安躺 不要想 地老天荒</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9be5376e6f7c99bc04b75097bd546847094f386","tid":446741,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T14:57:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾投票post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61a85bf62e491067c8e40259f35511497c41618","tid":4